This DVD features 16 songs from one of the 80's greatest musical performers. Includes hits such as "Turn This Mutha Out," "2 Legit 2 Quit," "Count It Off," "Pray" and more! Hammer was one of the pioneers of rap music--bringing it to the masses via his energetic and hyper-visual performaces. This collection of videos features of hits such as "U Can't Touch This", "Turn This Mutha Out", "Addams' Groove", and of course, "2 Legit 2 Quit". Also featured is a making of "Please Hammer Don't Hurt 'Em".
